{"tid":1690982,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我地真係好撚無用","createTime":"2019-11-03T13:04:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-03T13:50:26.000Z","uid":86136,"like":12,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"6b49561199d2bc00c6653b28562c1ac5bf01797e","tid":1690982,"uid":86136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T13:04:52.000Z","msg":"抗爭左4個月<br />\n不斷有手足被拉被消失受傷失去前途<br />\n<br />\n但仲未有狗被殺<br />\n何君堯個類擺到明做鳩我地既仲可以unun腳 有手有腳去happy hour<br />\n<br />\n4個月啦<br />\n咁就講時代革命<br />\n革命唔係企係到比人打 跑走架<br />\n係攞血同汗換架<br />\n<br />\n逐漸無人出都係我地一手做成<br />\nD狗都唔驚我地<br />\n因為我地做既野威脅唔到佢地<br />\n到時真係有做野既前線比人拉晒消失晒<br />\n成個運動就玩完了"},{"pid":"8416867244f05c732cd905ba148d819f3cc2bf9f","tid":1690982,"uid":86136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T13:05:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"70a16b4e118654bbb7175c9ab87a46fc6cd22221","tid":1690982,"uid":44019,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T13:05:53.000Z","msg":"拉"},{"pid":"fe0846d756fd0aa2ae77d43f2e28cb2f0a6a57f5","tid":1690982,"uid":149844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T13:05:57.000Z","msg":"半年了<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"307f25bf36631f93cb65e2e2055b15c081067e7a","tid":1690982,"uid":44019,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T13:06:08.000Z","msg":"拉"},{"pid":"9eeb5725f6d60a383bc922051a7d8c6e26bd6705","tid":1690982,"uid":86136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T13:06:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0ca2e33efb1e1e0855791448a72f2e2fc3b7dde6","tid":1690982,"uid":44019,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T13:06:19.000Z","msg":"拉"},{"pid":"d8d08248c268371e5dea32ec222bf3d769a74888","tid":1690982,"uid":42554,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03